Azure - Azure provides of cloud-based services like remote storage, database hosting, and centralized account management
Azure used to build, manage, and deploy applications on a massive global network using your favorite tools and frameworks.

Cloud Computing - is basic online CPU that provide service that you want 
Basic Services - 
           1. Computer power - compute power is service that provide the boost in compute for ex RAM in CPU but in Compute power you pay for services that you used 
            2. storage - storage is the used to store the large no of data like in CPU you have HardDisk but after some time HardDisk will full with data 
            but in cloud storage we will get as per storage you want as per busineess need and only pay or this same
            
           

          
